   {
    "en": "Introduction to Mineralogy"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "Mineral collecting is a modern-day treasure hunt!\n\nRuri, a high school girl who loves jewelry and accessories, ventures into the world of mineral collecting in mountains, rivers, and caves. The first volume features numerous minerals, including quartz, garnet, pyrite, gold sand, and fluorite. The collection scenes are full of fascinating scenes using specialized tools such as a panning dish, hammer, and topographical maps. This is an authentic science adventure based on the solid knowledge of the author, who is trained in mineralogy!",
   "ja": "宝石やアクセサリーが好きな女子高生ルリが、山へ川へ洞窟へ、鉱物採集の世界に飛び込んでいく。第1巻では、水晶、ガーネット、黄鉄鉱、砂金、蛍石など多数の鉱物が登場します。パニング皿、ハンマー、地形図など、専門的なツールを用いた採集シーンも魅力満載。"
  },
